{"tid":2143694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中美國防部長通電 管控危機防誤判","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T08:51:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f158e01a4ec9a588b0ec89b5a21a49ddffddc4d","tid":2143694,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200807/Z3SRSBADAA2FIWTPBFHLA4AFWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200807%2FZ3SRSBADAA2FIWTPBFHLA4AFWQ%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=80d251d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200807%2FZ3SRSBADAA2FIWTPBFHLA4AFWQ%2F&h=8817a988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200807/Z3SRSBADAA2FIWTPBFHLA4AFWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中美國防部長通電 管控危機防誤判<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SmEzBDRltJnaXfNIM9iG0rSmY9A=/640x460/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XPFWH7RG7XFKA4WX2POZYFPPTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSmEzBDRltJnaXfNIM9iG0rSmY9A%3D%2F640x460%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXPFWH7RG7XFKA4WX2POZYFPPTI.jpg&h=c27bea23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n075型兩棲攻擊艦昨出海試航。<br />\n<br />\n中美關係緊張，兩軍近日各自展示軍事實力，。。。。。。。。。。。。則向埃斯珀，表明中方在南海、台灣及美方「污名化」等問題上的原則立場，要求美方「停止錯誤言行」，加強海上風險管控，避免採取可能使局勢升溫的危險舉動，維護地區穩定。<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒昨發放「航母殺手」東風-26導彈的試射及快速應變演練情況，解放軍第一艘075型兩棲攻擊艦前日下午又正式出海試航。軍事評論員黃東向本報分析，反映官方現時積極備戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解放軍試射「航母殺手」<br />\n<br />\n075型兩棲攻擊艦一直被視為解放軍「登陸台灣」的最新武器，該艦前日下午約1點半時被人拍攝到，在拖船協助下離開上海滬東中華造船廠，沿着黃浦江進入東海水域，首度出海測試。根據中國媒體消息，今次試航或測試它的推進能力、島航與通訊等主要系統。《環球時報》英文版昨又公開了一條快速應變訓練片段，見到解放軍穿防護服走過染毒地區。軍人其後被告知有「衞星臨空」，然後完成車輛偽裝，最後發射東風-26攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報"},{"pid":"57e45504bb54f9951865e0b7029fff09f65b4d55","tid":2143694,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"約個時間開拖好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac5929866e8e4c8a23c27f507bd0a0d9ef542a5","tid":2143694,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e45504bb54f9951865e0b7029fff09f65b4d55","tid":2143694,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"約個時間開拖好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"支共一定玩偷襲<br />\neg 狼牙棒伏印度兵"},{"pid":"877ab4af3724cec51338ad0d3d485fce1ab06f72","tid":2143694,"uid":89857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"同美蘇熱線一樣<br />\n正常動作"}]}